@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Our story";
}


<div class="about-santa">
    <div class="about-santa__header">
        <h1 class="title">🎅 About Santa & His Reindeer 🦌</h1>
        <div class="subtitle">
            Santa Claus, also known as Saint Nicholas, has been delivering gifts to children around the world for centuries. His legendary sleigh is powered by magical
            reindeer, guiding him through snowy skies on Christmas Eve.
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="about-santa__raindeers">
        <h2 class="title">🦌 Meet Santa’s Reindeer</h2>
        <ul class="list">
            <li class="list__item"><span>Dasher</span> – The fastest reindeer, leading the way with speed and agility.</li>
            <li class="list__item"><span>Dancer</span> – A graceful performer, always ready to twirl through the skies.</li>
            <li class="list__item"><span>Prancer</span> – Elegant and strong, with a love for winter fun.</li>
            <li class="list__item"><span>Vixen</span> – Clever and quick-witted, always full of surprises.</li>
            <li class="list__item"><span>Comet</span> – The cool and calm navigator of the team.</li>
            <li class="list__item"><span>Cupid</span> – The bringer of love and holiday cheer.</li>
            <li class="list__item"><span>Donner</span> – Strong and bold, ready to power through snowstorms.</li>
            <li class="list__item"><span>Blitzen</span> – Lightning-fast and full of energy.</li>
            <li class="list__item"><span>Rudolph</span> – The famous red-nosed reindeer, leading Santa’s sleigh with his glowing nose.</li>
        </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="about-santa__prepare">
        <h2 class="title">🎄 How They Prepare for Christmas</h2>
        <div class="text">
            Santa’s reindeer spend the year training at the North Pole, staying in top shape for their big night. They eat magical oats, practice flying in winter
            storms, and even enjoy fun games to keep their spirits high!
        </div>
        <div class="text">
            On Christmas Eve, they gear up, get their bells polished, and wait for Santa’s signal to take off into the night sky, spreading joy across the world. 🎁✨
        </div>
    </div>
</div>